6. Development Workflow with Clarinet

A typical Clarinet workflow looks like:

Initialize a project with clarinet new.

Write your Clarity contracts in the contracts/ folder.

Write tests alongside in the tests/ folder.

Run a local blockchain and test interactions.

Deploy contracts to testnet or mainnet when ready. 
Stacks Documentaci√≥n

This structure encourages test-driven smart contract development and ensures your code is robust before real-world usage
